Nina Bo'nina Brown bụ aha ogbo nke Pierre Leverne Dease,  onye America na- eme ihe nkiri na omume telivishọn YouTube / eziokwu bụ onye batara mba ụwa na oge nke itoolu nke RuPaul Drag Race
A mụrụ Dease na July 12, 1982 na Columbia, South Carolina
Aha dragọn ya bụ "Beatta Bitchass" ruo mgbe ọ gbanwere ya ka ọ bụrụ Nina Bo'nina Brown
Ọ gbara akwụkwọ maka RuPaul Drag Race kemgbe oge ise
Ọ bụ onye na-ese ihe etemeete maka ụfọdụ n'ime anya Phi Phi O'Hara maka oru ngo "365 Days of Drag" ya
A mara ọkwa Brown dị ka otu n'ime ndị asọmpi iri na anọ na-asọ mpi na oge nke itoolu nke RuPaul Drag Race na February 2, 2017
Ọ bụ onye meriri n'ịma aka ihe nkiri mbụ ya na Lady Gaga dịka onye ọka ikpe ọbịa
N'ime ihe nkiri ise, o kwupụtara echiche ya na agaghị eme ya dị ka ihe nlereanya Blac Chyna maka ịma aka egwu
Ọ kpọrọ njem nlegharị anya 2018 ya "I shoulda Been Blac Chyna", ka oge a gachara
Drag Race Alumni Alaska tụkwara aka n'oge a n'ahịrị egwu ya "Valentina"
O tinyere n'ime ala abụọ ugboro atọ, na-ewepụ Aja na Valentina, tupu e wepụ onwe ya na ihe nkiri ahụ, mgbe ọ tụfuru egbugbere ọnụ nke " Cool for the Summer " nke Demi Lovato megide Shea Couleé
Na June 2018, MAC Cosmetics kwadoro ya iji nyochaa ma kwalite mkpokọta 2018 Aaliyah
Ọ na-eji ejiji dị ka zebra nke mmadụ na mbipụta July 2018 nke Akwụkwọ, na-eme ihe ngosi maka Gypsy Sport's Fall 2018 mkpọsa
Ọ kpụrụkwa ọzọ maka mkpọsa Gypsy Sport's Spring 2019
Brown nwetara aha ọma site na vidiyo YouTube ya biputere onwe ya na-enyocha ihe ngosi nke Drag Race ugbu a
Brown malitere nyochaa site na Episode 1, nke anọ oge kpakpando niile na Disemba 27, 2018
Na-aga n'ihu usoro webụ Rawview maka oge nke abụọ, Brown tụlere ihe omume kwa izu nke oge iri na otu malite na Maachị 2, 2019
Ya na Vanessa Vanjie Mateo pụtara maka akụkụ anọ nke usoro ịntanetị WOWPresents "Ejiji Foto RuView" n'etiti Nọvemba 2018 na Jenụwarị 2019, na-ejuputa maka Raja na Raven
Ọnwụ bụ n'ihu ọha nwoke nwere mmasị nwoke
Ọ na-alụ ọgụ na ịda mbà n'obi na nchekasị kemgbe ọ kwagara Atlanta, Georgia tupu ihe ngosi ahụ
Na RuPaul's Drag Race: Untucked, Dease kwuru na oge ọ na-agụ akwụkwọ maka oge 9 bụ oge ikpeazụ ọ ga-aga n'ihu, ebe ọ bụ na a jụrụ ajụjụ ya maka oge gara aga nke ihe ngosi ahụ
Dị ka Dease si kwuo, ọjụjụ ndị ahụ na-ekere òkè dị ukwuu n'imetụta ịda mbà n'obi na nchekasị ya
Na 2017, Nina Bo'nina Brown nwetara nzaghachi azụ maka izipu onye ofufe Valentina n'ụlọ na lipsync maka ndụ gị na ihe omume 9th nke oge itoolu nke RuPaul's Drag Race
Mwepụ ahụ gbadara dị ka otu n'ime ihe ngosi lipssync na-arụrịta ụka ma tinye ya na Gay Times Top 10 Kasị esemokwu RuPaul Drag Race Eliminations
Na 2021, Nina Bo'nina Brown boro ebubo na ọ na-ekwu okwu transphobic banyere Gottmik, onye na-asọmpi na oge iri na atọ nke RuPaul's Drag Race; Kade Gottlieb (aka Gottmik) bụ nwoke transgender

Okwu Brown, nke gụnyere njakịrị ugboro ugboro banyere nkwụsị nke Gottmik, kpalitere nkatọ sitere n'aka ọtụtụ ndị asọmpi RuPaul Drag Race, na ọtụtụ kpakpando na-agbachitere Gottmik, gụnyere Yvie Oddly, Jackie Cox, Denali, Kameron Michaels, na Jan Sport, yana Bimini Bon-Boulash
Joe Black, Cheryl Hole, na Crystal sitere na RuPaul Drag Race UK
Brown kwuru na nkatọ ahụ achọghị, na-agọnarị transphobia ọ bụla, ma kwuo na azụghachi azụ megide okwu ya bụ ịkagbu ọdịbendị
